  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play solo or with friends</strong></h2><br><i>Turbo Champ</i> is a fast-paced, arcade racing game. Unlock unique cars in the single-player campaign mode or play local matches with your friends.<br><br>You can even play online via Remote Play Together for game with <strong>2-4 players</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exciting game modes</strong></h2><br>Compete against friends in a classic <strong>Race</strong> game, battle over possession of a diamond in <strong>Tag</strong>, witness the questionable <strong>Bad Taxi</strong> game mode, and more! Turbo Champ has five unique game modes to choose from!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can play those games in quick matches, or in \"Tournament\" mode to prove you didn't just get lucky on that last match!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore new worlds</h2></strong><br><br>Zoom through the urban <strong>Downtown</strong>, descend the snowy <strong>Mountain</strong>, or zip through a lush <strong>Forest </strong>map. There are also battles to see in the Castle map, and new technology to witness out in the <strong>Space</strong> map.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each zone has a distinct style and <strong>unique features</strong> to keep things interesting from game to game!",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Play solo or with friends</strong></h2><br><i>Turbo Champ</i> is a fast-paced, arcade racing game. Unlock unique cars in the single-player campaign mode or play local matches with your friends.<br><br>You can even play online via Remote Play Together for game with <strong>2-4 players</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/39d6ea3f39f65f5d6e55ed83f177f91e.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Exciting game modes</strong></h2><br>Compete against friends in a classic <strong>Race</strong> game, battle over possession of a diamond in <strong>Tag</strong>, witness the questionable <strong>Bad Taxi</strong> game mode, and more! Turbo Champ has five unique game modes to choose from!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/06367ee20dfa3595f2900fbe378bfe02.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can play those games in quick matches, or in \"Tournament\" mode to prove you didn't just get lucky on that last match!<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore new worlds</h2></strong><br><br>Zoom through the urban <strong>Downtown</strong>, descend the snowy <strong>Mountain</strong>, or zip through a lush <strong>Forest </strong>map. There are also battles to see in the Castle map, and new technology to witness out in the <strong>Space</strong> map.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.poster.avif?t=1711751904\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.webm?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2658140/extras/3c5e019b92f794a07b67828d2569c795.mp4?t=1711751904\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each zone has a distinct style and <strong>unique features</strong> to keep things interesting from game to game!",
